MQTT Arduino client sends soil moisture data to the topic

# Raspberry Pi Mosquitto Broker Setup

Follow these steps to set up a Mosquitto MQTT broker on a Raspberry Pi:

Step 1: Update package lists
Use the following command to update the package lists on your Raspberry Pi:

sudo apt update

Step 2: Install Mosquitto MQTT broker package

sudo apt install mosquitto

Step 3: Start Mosquitto service:

sudo systemctl start mosquitto

Step 4: Verify Mosquitto service status:

systemctl status mosquitto
